A_410 - People are generally used to dealing with certain jobs thinking that they require a certain amount of effort. Regarding software development I can say that I have personally had very varied experiences with it, ranging from &ldquo;it's fun and easy to write this source code&rdquo; to &ldquo;this procedure is very difficult to develop&rdquo; to &ldquo;I feel like I'm exploring a place foggy, I don't even know if it will come to a solution&rdquo; ... but the truth is that this can probably happen with any job ...